Senzo Meyiwa's supporters outside court. Khulela Themba Sibiya, Bongani Sandiso Ntanzi, Mthobisi Chris Mncube, Mthokoziseni Zifozonke Mapisa and Sifiso Ntuli are facing charges of murder, attempted murder and robbery. Five suspects are accused of murdering the late Orlando Pirates and Bafana Bafana goalkeeper. Five suspects appeared in the Boksburg magistrate's court in connection with Senzo Meyiwa's murder. Senzo Meyiwa's supporters outside court. Khulela Themba Sibiya, Bongani Sandiso Ntanzi, Mthobisi Chris Mncube, Mthokoziseni Zifozonke Mapisa and Sifiso Ntuli are facing charges of murder, attempted murder and robbery. Five suspects are accused of murdering the late Orlando Pirates and Bafana Bafana goalkeeper. Five suspects appeared in the Boksburg magistrate's court in connection with Senzo Meyiwa's murder. Senzo Meyiwa's supporters outside court. Khulela Themba Sibiya, Bongani Sandiso Ntanzi, Mthobisi Chris Mncube, Mthokoziseni Zifozonke Mapisa and Sifiso Ntuli are facing charges of murder, attempted murder and robbery.